President Cyril Ramaphosa will use the third SA Investment Conference to ensure previous commitments are made a reality. This year's Investment Conference takes place amidst a pandemic that has further crippled South Africa's ailing economy. Editor’s note: The Livestream has ended. You may watch the recording above. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa delivers the opening address at the South Africa Investment Conference. The conference is part of expanding SA’s efforts to grow domestic and international investment. 